parameters:
\nc<Lewd Demon Employee>Ah, Saki! That research institute you often went to on
dispatch... there's been a huge incident.
\bustMsgExp[1, 1]\nc<Saki>Eh? What happened to the research institute?

\nc<Lewd Demon Employee>Apparently, a certain streamer did some undercover reporting
and uncovered something scandalous. Our company is involved
too, and the atmosphere is really tense right now.

\nc<Lewd Demon Employee>There won't be any dispatch work for a while... Well, maybe
that's a good thing for you, Saki?

\nc<Senpai>It'll quiet down soon enough. If the company was going to
collapse over this, it wouldn't have lasted until today.

\nc<Senpai>Do you know how much investment that research institute
receives in a year? I'm sure the bigwigs will try
desperately to cover it up.

\nc<Senpai>That streamer will probably be slapped with all sorts of
charges and sued... Poor thing.

\nc<Senpai>You all should stop chattering and get back to work. Fewer
dispatch locations mean fewer places to squeeze profits
from.
